{"tid":1353810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"方皓玟新歌《願》為港人打氣:「希望用力量化成音樂，和大家共進退，記錄這時艱。」","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T09:17:24.000Z","uid":9030,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"35c5e58ef7e744f7cbdf7b0eeed0a7022bf82bda","tid":1353810,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"方皓玟:<br />\n最近心情真的百感交集，對於這片土地我們都這麼熱愛和着緊，現實實在令人心痛。製作這首歌的時候，有千言萬語想表達，拍MV更哽咽多次。而每當變幻時，我都希望能用微細的力量化成音樂，和大家共進退，記錄這時艱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B0PfEtjH9VU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0PfEtjH9VU%2F&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=be8df93e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0PfEtjH9VU%2F&h=2040f205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B0PfEtjH9VU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4zNaEukzyGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4zNaEukzyGk&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=2bba4fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4zNaEukzyGk</a>"},{"pid":"882df2c9aad3250a9f21f27006370a4c2ea264d2","tid":1353810,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"願<br />\n<br />\n作曲：林家謙<br />\n作詞：方皓玟<br />\n編曲：許創基/孔奕佳<br />\n監製：許創基<br />\n主唱：方皓玟"},{"pid":"726a81429ff8e98988e1c965848c78474502d05c","tid":1353810,"uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"願世間都珍惜信望愛  能相愛<br />\n奉上一生光陰去競賽<br />\n誰亦不必爭議  不需對峙<br />\n明日縱使跌低  寧願抗爭到底<br />\n<br />\n願世間都擺低對罵戰和偏見<br />\n願你聽取心聲與異見<br />\n明日不需槍炮  只需對話<br />\n蒙著眼的那位  難避戰火的洗禮<br />\n<br />\n問世上還有幾多人  甦醒一個靈魂<br />\n願我們能有理想息紛爭再放下怒憤<br />\n沒法能忘記這天絢麗白色哀傷的日期<br />\n萬世正等你<br />\n<br />\n話我知蒼天想試煉您  求真理<br />\n話我知應該怎哀悼你<br />\n沈默不可解決  青春歲月<br />\n承諾太早說穿  隨便轉更加倉促<br />\n<br />\n問世上還有幾多人   枯萎一個靈魂<br />\n願我們能有理想息紛爭再放下怒憤<br />\n沒法能忘記這天絢麗白色我們來過此<br />\n一起行多遠   想說<br />\n問世上還有幾多人  睜得開眼沈睡去<br />\n為你而流過那些幸福的眼淚<br />\n沒法能忘記這天千鈞一髮是你微細身軀<br />\n豁得出去<br />\n用愛緊抱自由  願覺醒再無內鬥  <br />\n願你終於清醒 有沒有"},{"pid":"2103d31379aba805c9aacee152d015a58b6c643b","tid":1353810,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Woo0qAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWoo0qAQ.jpg&h=05b96831&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b2b4b60e39685c36a397c3f7583b54c65a24408","tid":1353810,"uid":251820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8f62c4100d6824a0aa935262e69db7e0ac69e7","tid":1353810,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"19801c348fb9ffc2d0b2f614da67506345b2a52a","tid":1353810,"uid":11580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdfc2c3f99064891b629129e3c1723cdabcb9f7","tid":1353810,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19801c348fb9ffc2d0b2f614da67506345b2a52a","tid":1353810,"uid":11580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c00a71f73c0b8a84d2f01185e87094e58e3bef9","tid":1353810,"uid":125553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc